          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">
          <strong>Net Worth:</strong> $14.6 billion</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">
          <strong>Rank:</strong> 109th in the world today</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">
          <strong>About:</strong> Founder of Geely Automobile, Li revolutionized China's automotive industry by introducing affordable yet quality vehicles. He took bold steps by acquiring global brands like Volvo and a significant stake in Daimler (Mercedes-Benz). His focus on electric cars positioned Geely as a leader in green transportation. Despite operating in the shadows of Tesla and other giants, Li’s influence reshaped global car markets.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">
          <strong>Need to Know:</strong> Li surprised the industry with his daring Volvo acquisition, which was once ridiculed but is now hailed as a masterstroke. Known for being reclusive, Li keeps his personal life under wraps while quietly shaping the industry. ​</p>
          
